default.source:
<style>
.menuopen {
  max-height: 200px !important;
  overflow: hidden !important;
  transition: max-height 0.5s ease;
}

.menuclose {
  max-height: 0 !important;
  overflow: hidden !important;
  transition: max-height 0.5s ease;
}

.menuopenData {
  max-height: 300px !important;
  overflow: hidden !important;
  transition: max-height 0.5s ease;
}

.menucloseData {
  max-height: 0 !important;
  overflow: hidden !important;
  transition: max-height 0.5s ease;
}

.sidebaropen{
  max-width: 240px !important;
  overflow: hidden !important;
  transition: max-width 1s ease;
}

.sidebarclose{
  max-width: 80px !important;
  overflow: hidden !important;
  transition: max-width 1s ease;
}

.sidebarclose .ww-text-content {
  opacity: 0;
  width: 0;
  overflow: hidden;
  pointer-events: none;
}

.arrow{
  transition: 
    left 1s ease,
    transform 1s ease;
}

.sidebaropen ~ .arrow {
  left: 230px !important;
  transform: translateY(-50%) scaleX(-1);
}

.sidebarclose ~ .arrow {
  left: 70px !important;
  transform: translateY(-50%) scaleX(1);
}

</style>
